in your geany you can paste this setup below

1. Go in build -> set builds commands
2. compile = C:\User\Name\Python\Python38-32
3. lint = pep8 --max-line-length=80 "%f"
4. error regular expression = (.+):([0-9]+):([0-9]+)
5. contruir = make
6. make custom target = make
7. contruir object = make %e.o
8. execute  = Python "%f"
